    "raw_text": "Employment\nWho We Are\nAwards and Recognitions\nOpen Jobs\nOpen to Public\nInternal Postings\nApply for Internships with the Commonwealth\nApply for Fellowships with the Commonwealth\nOur Fellows\nApply for Apprenticeships with the Commonwealth\nCareers for Federal Employees\nOur Benefits\nOur Team, Our Benefits\nHealth and Wellness\nWork Life Balance\nFinancial Security\nGrowth and Development\nCareer Development\nEducation Benefits\nLifestyle & Wellness Perks\nApplication Support\nFAQs\nPolicies\nResidency Guidelines\nRecruitment Events\nVeterans\nVeterans’ Preference\nAgencies\nEmployment\nFind Your Passion for Public Service!\nYour Career with the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania Starts Here\nSearch openings, explore careers, and apply today.\nView all job openings\nExplore Career Paths\nYour Experience Matters\nAt the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, we value your skills and experience. Currently, 92% of state government jobs are open to skilled Pennsylvanians without a four-year degree. That’s 65,000 opportunities available to you.\nExplore our central hub to browse job titles that don’t require a degree.\nBrowse Jobs\nInternships, Apprenticeships, and Fellowships\nJumpstart your career with opportunities where you will be part of impactful projects, learn from lifelong mentors, and grow in a supportive community that values your career development.\nExplore our programs\nExplore Popular Job Categories\nView all job openings\nHealthcare\nHelp improve lives and make a difference.\nView Jobs in Healthcare\nEducation\nShape the future by teaching and inspiring.\nView more\nEngineering\nInnovate and build the world  around us.\nView more\nPublic Safety\nProtect and serve your community.\nView more\nInformation Technology\nDrive progress through technology and innovation.\nView more\nEnvironmental Services\nPreserve and protect our natural resources.\nView more\nWhy Work With Us?\nOur benefits package is designed to support your overall well-being, helping you thrive both at work and in life.\nFinancial Security:\nRetirement plans and financial planning resources.\nPhysical Health:\nComprehensive health insurance and fitness incentives.\nMental Wellness:\nCounseling services and wellness programs.\nWonder how these benefits work in real life? Our team members share their experiences. Discover how our benefits can help you succeed both personally and professionally.\nExplore our benefits\nSee our benefits through our stories\nOur Commitment to Diversity & Inclusion\nAt the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, we believe that a diverse and inclusive workplace is essential for innovation, growth, and the success of our public service mission. We are committed to fostering an environment where every employee feels valued, respected, and empowered to contribute their unique perspectives and talents. Our dedication to diversity, equity, and inclusion ensures that we not only reflect the communities we serve but also create a culture where all voices are heard and everyone has the opportunity to thrive.\nCelebrating Excellence\nWe’re proud to be recognized as a top employer, highlighting our commitment to a supportive and innovative workplace. These awards reflect our dedication to excellence and employee well-being.\nOur Achievements\nContact Us\nHave questions or need assistance? We're here to help.\nEmail\nGet Job Alerts\nFollow us on social media.\nsocial media channels Like\nsocial media channels Follow",
